sequenceDiagram
    participant Script as demo_exec_scenario.sh
    participant VM as Lima VM
    participant EX as Extrapolator Cron
    participant RT as EDAMAME Runtime

    Script->>VM: start_services
    Script->>EX: enable_fast_cron (*/2 min; prod */5)
    Script->>RT: wait for baseline model + telemetry cycle
    Note over RT: Internal loops: divergence/intent, vulnerability/safety-floor, advisor/remediation; prod default 300 s, demo 60 s

    loop Each Scenario
        Script->>VM: inject_<threat>()
        Script->>VM: wait_for_session + wait_for_l7
        Note over EX,RT: extrapolator reads session history and publishes intent slice; explicit-slice benchmarks bypass this lane
        Note over RT: divergence correlates intent vs telemetry; vulnerability evaluates model-independent guardrails
        Note over RT: internal alerting routes actionable divergence findings (Telegram, Slack)
        Script->>RT: poll get_divergence_verdict
        Script->>Script: assert verdict
        Script->>VM: cleanup_<threat>()
        Script->>Script: write_scenario_artifacts
    end

    Script->>EX: restore_production_cron
